Histoire du prince et de son cheval (English: "Akụkọ banyere nwa eze na ịnyịnya ya") bụ akụkọ ọdịnala nke oge a nke onye edemede Gillaume Spitta-Bey chịkọtara na ngwụcha narị afọ nke 19
Wallis Budge sụgharịrị ya dịka Akụkọ nke Prince na ịnyịnya ya. Onye Ọwụwa Anyanwụ J
Mardrus gụnyere akụkọ ahụ dịka The Eleventh Captain's Tale na nsụgharị ya nke The Arabian Nights, n'agbanyeghị na ọ bụghị akụkụ nke ederede mbụ nke nchịkọta ahụ.
A na-ahazi akụkọ ahụ na Aarne-Thompson-Uther Index nke mba ụwa dịka ụdị ATU 314, "Goldener", yana ihe mmeghe ọzọ: ajọ nne na ịnyịnya na-akpagbu dike na ịgba ịta ya
A maara akụkọ yiri nke ahụ n'ofe North Africa na Middle East.
A mụrụ nwa nwoke nke sultan na nwa ehi n'otu oge, nne ha nwụkwara
enyere nwa eze nwa ehi ahụ, onye na - azụ ma na-enye ya nri mgbe ọ bụla o si n'ụlọ akwụkwọ lọta
Iji belata iru uju ya, sultan lụrụ nwanyị ọzọ
Nwunye ọhụrụ nke sultan (nke bụbu nwa agbọghọ ohu), Otú ọ dị, nwere onye hụrụ ya n'anya, onye Juu, ha abụọ kpara ajọ nkata igbu nwa nwoke nwunye di ya

Otu ụbọchị, ịnyịnya ahụ bere ákwá ma kwupụtara nwa eze ahụ, aha ya bụ Mohammed L'Avisé ("Clever Mohammed"; "Muhammad the Clever One", na nsụgharị Wallis Budge), banyere atụmatụ aghụghọ nke nwunye nna ya igbu ya site na itinye nsí na nri ya
Otú ọ dị, mgbe ịnyịnya ahụ dọrọ aka ná ntị, nwa eze ahụ nyere nwamba nri ahụ nwere nsí, nke riri ya ma nwụọ.
